#      - Available: tl2=36
#      - Required: tl2≥50
#      - Gap: 14 units short
# 
#   8. Circular dependency: Need tl1 to produce tl2, but insufficient tl1
#      to produce enough tl2 for required consumer tasks → UNSAT

